    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of any wear, with all electronics and features functioning perfectly. This car has been garage-kept and has a full service history, making it a rare find for any collector or enthusiast seeking perfection.",
