    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is nothing short of meticulous. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to original factory specifications, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality asset. We invite you to experience this definitive example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
