    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s in truly flawless condition. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving perfection. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring a reinforced subframe and documented preventative rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry is preserved via factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring the variable M differential lock translates power with surgical precision. Exterior finish exhibits zero orange peel or clear coat failure, while the cabin retains its original matte leather texture and structural bolster integrity. This is a mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
