    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-ready vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. It has been exclusively garage-kept under a breathable cover and only hand-washed using professional-grade products. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creases or bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, toggle, and digital display functions perfectly, with zero fading or wear on the touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not just a used vehicle; it is a meticulously preserved specimen suitable for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
